{"tid":314602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[法律JJ召喚]有無巴/絲熟或知道小額錢債同審判過程","createTime":"2017-07-09T11:12:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-13T08:43:41.000Z","uid":107075,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2d79a528fa4ee35173e7649c8045a6a50364e624","tid":314602,"uid":107075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T11:12:57.000Z","msg":"細路易信人，早半年借左錢比人 <br />\n人地之前無工返無摧人還住 <br />\n到人地有工開時我搵返佢，想佢還錢時就咩聯絡都block曬我 <br />\n就算上門搵佢屋企人同佢一樣賴皮 <br />\n我有欠單係手對方都講明一個仙都唔還架喇 <br />\n<br />\n昨日正式已入紙小額錢債小額錢債審裁處等上庭 <br />\n想知上庭時除左好似審裁處指示帶欠單比個官睇之外 <br />\n我仲有無其它要準備乜野 <br />\n仲有上庭時我除左對住個官之外，在場仲有無其它人係度 <br />\n聽聞過審判官態度好差，咁唔好彩遇上我要點做？"},{"pid":"cc2b10f33358818481d4a4344bc0dc7597a83382","tid":314602,"uid":2436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T11:14:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6f4c61865d3444afd1e505baae995f66acdae431","tid":314602,"uid":69855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T11:21:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2634e255e299a5aea2de3e204fd7f02265d80555","tid":314602,"uid":107075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T11:46:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n咁就底你死，賣埋層樓打官司啦垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴係唔係搞錯左，我係借錢比人果個喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋上小額都預都追唔到筆數<br />\n係唔想比個無賴同無賴一家咁得戚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68a6fa3a334beca21558a925a9e7b2ba9fe01392","tid":314602,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T11:51:48.000Z","msg":"有堆人借錢的時候乜都得，還的時候惡過鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0a9e2c7aa29356d021d5eb58e657e2cbf9edfdd","tid":314602,"uid":107075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T11:52:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://www.courts.ca.gov/partners/documents/smallclaimschecklist-ch.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.courts.ca.gov%2Fpartners%2Fdocuments%2Fsmallclaimschecklist-ch.pdf&d=EMnXzwzI9%2BVdAAo0RcKNFUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=d9492413\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.courts.ca.gov/partners/documents/smallclaimschecklist-ch.pdf</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n蔣巴<br />\n我係香港人，想要香港例<br />\n上面份野台灣架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd2602d93750e10248c10b86d0307b60bf98a916","tid":314602,"uid":107075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T11:55:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有堆人借錢的時候乜都得，還的時候惡過鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正正係咁&hellip;<br />\n借果時實牙實齒會還<br />\n過左關就拖，拖完又拖<br />\n再問直頭唔想認數<br />\n仲要對方屋企家人完全唔想理<br />\n有咩你就追返佢，我咩都唔知，勁無賴<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n巴有無認識朋友上過去？"},{"pid":"4e5c4955908fb216ace4a153e461f36933486a91","tid":314602,"uid":36300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T11:55:58.000Z","msg":"好簡單"},{"pid":"aed56cd4524caa386f95352b8bfb268ea0f7c437","tid":314602,"uid":107075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T12:04:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好簡單</blockquote><br />\n巴上過去？<br />\n求詳細"},{"pid":"b6d75dd4cd3a36aa0d989c9af82b71025b46fcbc","tid":314602,"uid":107075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T13:19:31.000Z","msg":"求助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c91e66c3394d775ea034db680792d0c9e5dbc4ab","tid":314602,"uid":69855,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T14:05:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2ccd1e575eff227b53a558720220959ae8e6a99a","tid":314602,"uid":69855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T14:08:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"84ce5c171ea195fb775cad52bf0f52469c0f93a8","tid":314602,"uid":107075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T14:19:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"http://www.courts.ca.gov/partners/documents/smallclaimschecklist-ch.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.courts.ca.gov%2Fpartners%2Fdocuments%2Fsmallclaimschecklist-ch.pdf&d=EMnXzwzI9%2BVdAAo0RcKNFUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=d9492413\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.courts.ca.gov/partners/documents/smallclaimschecklist-ch.pdf</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n蔣巴<br />\n我係香港人，想要香港例<br />\n上面份野台灣架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n收皮啦，台灣例可以用係法律度，唔識唔好扮勁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係香港法律度啊，屌你老母</blockquote><br />\n我唔知道點解你態度咁差<br />\n不過都想問點解台灣法律可以用係香港度<br />\n屌你老母"},{"pid":"19a230f9894f95ff4393bba3181ea6428cb654d8","tid":314602,"uid":69855,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T14:29:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1658062f80a1efeea6d5ba350d5f2776bc3ce432","tid":314602,"uid":6192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T14:37:18.000Z","msg":"小額最開頭係見調解員 主任果d先<br />\n會睇下你地傾唔傾得掂先<br />\n經過4次調解都解決唔到先會見官<br />\n不過如果對方唔上就會直接判你win <br />\n不過就算你win都唔代表佢會還錢<br />\n債仔一樣可以wfc 個判決<br />\n只係如果你win左<br />\n可以進一步申請佢破產逼佢還錢<br />\n但你申請佢破產你係比錢出黎的"},{"pid":"56becfb8bd2f3ba6e633cc14e660740588124bb4","tid":314602,"uid":69855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T14:39:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7c02e10cf62d1a128f58f1a13c4e9a346abca74f","tid":314602,"uid":2436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T14:40:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a9af90407df81bedfd700fd8a236a0681c35381a","tid":314602,"uid":2436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T14:40:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6a19f53523e3c6a8dc363f65243b2f21a2cb761c","tid":314602,"uid":2436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T14:40:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aa2806844cbad0eb4167cda44e2e6ccd025df8db","tid":314602,"uid":2436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T14:41:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"767e3d042db16813dd00d954954a5630f89b772f","tid":314602,"uid":69855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T14:43:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3b27703133febd233d450379087bcfb4f5dd4080","tid":314602,"uid":2436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T14:45:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1cc655512efd4e79955046b3d8df9a58864da84a","tid":314602,"uid":2436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T14:48:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9b62216cbdf08a1b0b58c8ef64e2a36d5e31e497","tid":314602,"uid":69855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T14:48:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f94c184e611dcc314b323bf7df38d1ebc62892ee","tid":314602,"uid":107075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T15:31:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小額最開頭係見調解員 主任果d先<br />\n會睇下你地傾唔傾得掂先<br />\n經過4次調解都解決唔到先會見官<br />\n不過如果對方唔上就會直接判你win <br />\n不過就算你win都唔代表佢會還錢<br />\n債仔一樣可以wfc 個判決<br />\n只係如果你win左<br />\n可以進一步申請佢破產逼佢還錢<br />\n但你申請佢破產你係比錢出黎的</blockquote><br />\n對方無賴黎，九成都傾唔掂<br />\n借完而家都可以唔應借過，同屋企人串嘴返轉頭<br />\n就算告得入到時認完都可以串嘴唔還<br />\n申請破佢產要皮幾野，唉"}]}